c
c Conversion of TREAT reactor model with M8-Cal created by A. W. LaPorta

c --- Full Core ---
c
c  fc26 (n) energy deposition in core (MeV/g)
c  f26:n (100700<100800)
c  sd26 1  $ Convert MeV/g to total MeV
c c
c  fc36 (p) energy deposition in core (MeV/g)
c  f36:p (100700<100800)
c  sd36 1  $ Convert MeV/g to total MeV
c c
c  fc9984      fission density for core fuel (fiss/cc)
c  fm9984     -1 999 -6
c  f9984:n    (3000 11000 12000 13000 14000 15000 16000)
c             (20000 21000 22000 23000)
c             (30000 31000 32000 33000)
